Uses of Package
com.esri.mo2.data.feat

Packages that use com.esri.mo2.data.feat
com.esri.mo2.data.feat Classes that represent the ESRI data model. 
com.esri.mo2.data.omc Supports caching of objects. 
com.esri.mo2.file.shp Support for accessing ESRI shapefiles. 
com.esri.mo2.map.core Defines Layout, Map, and MapElement-related interfaces that could be implemented as either visual or non-visual components. 
com.esri.mo2.map.dpy Support for major Map components. 
com.esri.mo2.map.draw Classes used for rendering vector data. 
com.esri.mo2.map.elt Provides classes and interfaces for a common set of map elements that can be added directly or indirectly to either UI-based or non-UI-based ElementContainer(s). 
com.esri.mo2.map.img Classes that are used for communicating with ESRI ArcIMS components for all current versions. 
com.esri.mo2.map.mem Classes that provide a way to construct in-memory Layers and FeatureClasses. 
com.esri.mo2.ui.bean Java beans and associated classes. 
com.esri.mo2.ui.lyt Contains the visual components of the layout framework application. 
com.esri.mo2.util This package has various utility classes that couldn't easily be classified.
